ing: 1 pinch ground cinnamon, or to taste
2 tablespoons whipped cream, or more to taste
des: "This milkshake is a delectable treat! It's creamy, rich, and sweet. I recommend this for a morning drink! Enjoy! xoxo, Chef Nilla&Poptart"
ins: Combine milk, ice cream, banana, and cinnamon in a blender; blend on low speed until consistency of a thick milkshake. Pour milkshake into a cup and top with whipped cream and drizzled caramel.
